column1: ##FileFormat = OSCtable (sort of)
##ColumnVariable[Name] = Library name to be used in expression tables, etc.
##ColumnVariable[LSA_Name] = Library name used in the LS-Archive record.
##ColumnVariable[Rev] = Protocol revision on ScriptHub (A or B).
##ColumnVariable[LibID] = LS-Archive library identifier.
##ColumnVariable[Sequence_Run_ID] = HiSeq sequence run identifier.
##ColumnVariable[Lane] = Lane number in the HiSeq run.
##ColumnVariable[Reads] = Number of reads passing filter.
##ColumnVariable[PF] = Percentage of reads passing filter (from total).
##ColumnVariable[C1_Run_ID] = C1 run identifier (serial number of the C1 array).
##ColumnVariable[PC] = 96-well plate coordinate of the sample replaced by the positive control.
##ColumnVariable[NC] = 96-well plate coordinate of the sample replaced by the negative control.
##ColumnVariable[t00] = Color code of time point 0 hours.
##ColumnVariable[t06] = Color code of time point 6 hours.
##ColumnVariable[t24] = Color code of time point 24 hours.
##ColumnVariable[Curation] = Initials of curator : what was curated.
##ColumnVariable[Moirai_Stamp] = Timestamp of Moirai processing (OP-WORKFLOW-CAGEscan-short-reads-v2.0)
